00:26:41.380 --> 00:26:42.850
to us frequently, we
never use garlic.

00:26:42.850 --> 00:26:44.150
Ew, garlic.

00:26:44.150 --> 00:26:46.030
You know. [Inaudible] us
villagers only use onion.

00:26:46.030 --> 00:26:48.980
And so it was really remarkable
